 </span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:12pt">priorities </span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:12pt">that </span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:12pt">meet local needs and lever in economic development</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:12pt">. </span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:12pt">F</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:12pt">ewer funding pots mean</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:12pt">t a</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:12pt"> less silo based approach to transport funding and a more integrated approach to solutions.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 21.3pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:-21.3pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:12pt">2.</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:12pt">              </span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:12pt">For the period beyond 2015, Major Scheme funding and prioritisation was de</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:12pt">volved to Local Transport Bodies</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:12pt"> </span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:12pt">(LTB)</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:12pt"> </span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:12pt">constit</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:12pt">ut</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:12pt">ed of </span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:12pt">Local Enterprise Partnerships (</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:12pt">LEP</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:12pt">)</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:12pt">,</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:12pt"> Integrated Transport Authorities (</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:12pt">ITA</span><span style="font-family:Calib